p.d: Manateq Qatar Cross-Country Rally signalled the opening round of the FIA World Cup for Cross-Country Rallies at the stunning, awe-inspiring state of Qatar. Organised by the Qatar Motor and Motorcycle Federation (QMMF), the event attracted 33 teams and competitors from 17 nations. 5 days of intense competition and 1,444.99 kilometres in the challenging Qatar desert, tested cars and drivers to their limits.
